GitHub Copilot AI for Selenium WebDriver Java Tests/Framework
Assistance

IDE Used: JetBrains IntelliJ

AI Capabilities:

1) Create new files (Page Objects, Tests, etc) following the format of
   existing files.

2) Generate Selenium action methods with accurate locators using HTML
   input.

3) Understand project hierarchy and establish connections across
   multiple file.

4) Identify and fix error from project

5) Search for and retrieve method usage and implementations files
   within the project.

6) Add necessary comments and documentation to improve code readability.

7) Convert automation code into plain english language manual test case

8) Optimize the test code based on PR comments in peer retired pull
   request

9) Generate step definition for cucumber and also helps to create
   feature file
